Texts.Chs:
一罐鸡汤。它拥有小巧的包装，是补充水份和身体含盐量的绝佳来源，尽管它还不如鸡肉玉米浓汤好吃。但不管怎样，你总得试一下。
^orange;类型：熟肉食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
A can of Chicken Soup. A great source of hydration and bodily salt content in a small, compact package. It's just not as good as chicken-corn-chowder though. You gotta try that sometime.
^orange;Type: Cooked Meat^reset;
